    "**Answer (4a):** The predicted map successfully reconstructs the broad geographic distribution of the tribes, showing that genetic markers are strong predictors of latitude and longitude. However, this map provides a highly optimistic view of the model's performance. Since the PCA and the linear regression were both fitted and evaluated on the same dataset, we are observing the \"training error\" rather than the \"generalization error\".  \n",
